{"about_the_game":"MistsBook is a roguelike game that combines deck building and autobattler design, created by the independent game team <strong>Dehist</strong> from China.<br><br>You are drinking in a bar when suddenly a beautiful girl sits down opposite you. She gives you a mysterious smile and hands you a book, telling you that if you flip to the last page of this book, she will grant you a request.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><strong>Ultimate deck building</strong><br>Each time, you will choose at least three sets of decks to start the game.  There are matching mechanisms waiting for you to explore between each set of decks, allowing you to build decks that generate as much energy as possible during the game.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2708720/extras/Play_EN.gif?t=1733479685\" /><br><br><strong>Auto Battler? </strong><br>Just click the button to enjoy the synergy effect between the cards you carefully configure. In each turn, you will have the chance to adjust the order of your cards or keep them in your hand.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2708720/extras/Op_EN.gif?t=1733479685\" /><br><br><strong>Floral Seals</strong><br>Want to keep a certain card in your hand?  Want to enhance the power of a certain card?  Want to control the order of certain cards?  Floral seals will meet your expectations.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2708720/extras/Seal_EN.gif?t=1733479685\" /><br><br><strong>Mysterious Patterns</strong><br>You will have the opportunity to obtain powerful mists cards, which may be the real core of your deck building.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2708720/extras/Mist_EN.gif?t=1733479685\" /><br><br><strong>Unique Symbols</strong><br>Each symbol will enhance the ene